Hi,

I downloaded the latest version today ( 8 apr 2006 ). I am using the ARDatabind attribute. Because I have a nested instance it calls ShouldRecreateInstance on the ARDatabinder. The problem is it is a new activerecord instance, so the first parameter to this function call is empty. In this case ShouldRecreateInstance fails. I have solved this bug in my own copy by adding this line at the top of ShouldRecreateInstance:

if ( value == null ) return true;
